          SECTION 1.0 PURPOSE          ___________________


          The purpose  of these  network specifications  is to  provide a
          detailed description of the customer's network from an external
          viewpoint.  This includes the operational and performance char-
          acteristics of the network.  These specifications are the basis
          for the acceptance criteria and the acceptance test procedure.

          A TYMNET network provides tools, technology, and flexibility to
          enhance, develop and implement a  customer's current and future
          network requirements.  These tools provide  the network manage-
          ment staff  with the information  necessary to  monitor network
          problems in real time,  and the ability to plan  for the expan-
          sion of the network.








































