               figured in the  Pilot Test Procedure, and,  thereafter, as
               mutually agreed to by the customer and Tymshare.

            o  Perform,  with the  aid of  Tymshare, the  Pilot Test  and
               Acceptance Tests.   The customer will supervise  the Pilot
               Test and Acceptance  Tests and may request  the assistance
               of Tymshare in performing these tests.

            o  Provide all the operational functions required by the net-
